#### SU10 (Mass User Maintenance)

- It let the administrator perform bulk operations on user accounts (Create, Modify, Lock/Unlock, Assign roles, delete, change passwords).

- This a critical transaction used by security administrators.
- SU10 applies changes in bulk, we need to use it caution and test changes in non-productive environmnent.

